MatchedRegions.transcript: My name is Bonifat Stur, and today we present our work, Carlane, a lane detection benchmark for unsupervised domain adaptation from simulation to multiple real-world domains.

MatchedRegion.Text: CARLANE: A Lane Detection Benchmark for Unsupervised Domain Adaptation from Simulation to multiple Real-World Domains

MatchedRegions.transcript: This is joint work with Johann Haselberger and Julian Gebele.
